HEADWORD: Rooted
<hw>Root"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having taken root; firmly
implanted; fixed in the heart.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>rooted</xex>
sorrow.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

